{
  "stem": "12494.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People went to their deaths without believing that they are going to their death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was-- there was a degree of non-belief, a degree of-- of, well, it couldn't happen here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite irrational.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's difficult to understand today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's difficult for me to understand that it was not clear to us that the same thing will sooner or later happen to us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how it is possible that we believed that Hitler is just going to let little Hungary play its games, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] ostensibly cooperating with him, but really not suppressing their Jews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's what people hoped for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My dad had a visa for Palestine in 1939, which he didn't use.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got a certificate to Palestine in 1943 from Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kasztner.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who had a few available.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I didn't use it, because my dad objected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't-- he didn't want his son to go too-- too-- too far away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted to keep his son around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rezso Kasztner-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kasztner was, in effect, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one of the two or three real heads of the Zionist movement in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's a complicated story, because I say Hungary, and the boundaries of Hungary changed almost year after year.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In 1940, Hitler made a decision to return to Hungary, from Romania, the northern part of Transylvania, which was lost by Hungary to Romania in 1918-- 1920, really, officially.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with that, a large number of Romanian Jews suddenly became Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rezso Kasztner belonged to that category of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He came from Cluj [INAUDIBLE], which was the capital of that particular area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's a complicated story too.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
